    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>drained sweetcorn</strong> to the pan and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to char</p><p>Once staring to char, add the <strong>chopped tomato</strong> and <strong>diced onion</strong> and cook for 3-4 min further or until starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 6,
